      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 31.1 - 老子 31.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 31.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫佳兵者，不祥之器，物或惡之，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Now arms, however beautiful, are instruments of evil omen, hateful, it may be said, to all creatures.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-031__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-031</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
