      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 31.14 - 老子 31.15</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 31.9 - 老子 31.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫樂殺人者，則不可以得志於天下矣。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>and he who delights in the slaughter of men cannot get his will in the kingdom. On occasions of festivity to be on the left hand is the prized position;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-031__align-010">
