      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 31.23 - 老子 31.24</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 31.16</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>戰勝，以喪禮處之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>and the victor in battle has his place (rightly) according to those rites.</seg>
      </tuv>
